{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1731719299.696005", "card_id": "Q_4078010020", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 136}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "审稿人强行要求引用 13 篇无关文章，中科院金属所在引言「硬刚」，如何评价这一行为？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "文章 DOI"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8285c9fcf2da3261e2f2557e550388da_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "296 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4078010020"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIgaaLkdWe2o40EAMaCTExMTc5MjE1OSDHydK5BjAAONUFQAByCjQwNzgwMTAwMjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1731719299.696537", "card_id": "Q_3833350017", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 149}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "福州教育局制定局长陪餐制，每月不少于一次，如何看待此举？能有效避免食堂食品安全事故吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "央广网福州 11 月 10 日消息（记者罗晓英）记者 10 日从福州市教育局获悉，为强化中小学、幼儿园食品安全管理，严格落实食品安全和膳食经费管理专项整治工作，预防食品安全和食堂管理事故，福州市教育局制定局长陪餐制。陪餐人员为市县两级教育局局长，分管副局长、机关处（科）室负责人；陪餐对象为全市中小学、幼儿园食堂或者从校外供餐单位订购食品向学生提供餐饮服务的中小学校。原则上陪餐人员每月到中小学、幼儿园陪餐不少于一次。 内容来源福州市建立教育局局长陪餐工作机制 _ 管理 _ 中小学 _ 幼儿园"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b6b0e7802813716c9cd365de322fcf5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "151 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3833350017"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIgaaLkdWe2o40EAMaCTExMTc0MzM2NSCD28W5BjAAOLcBQAFyCjM4MzMzNTAwMTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1731719299.697875", "card_id": "Q_4229812089"